g.title: t1

g.title: t12
g.text: sum(CAST(val AS BIGINT)) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)

g.title: t2
g.text: sum(val) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val ASC NULLS FIRST ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND 1 FOLLOWING)

g.title: t3
g.text: count(val) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN 1 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)

g.title: t4
g.text: sum(val) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 1 FOLLOWING)

g.title: t5
g.text: sum(val_long) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val_long ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 2147483648 FOLLOWING)

g.title: t6
g.text: sum(val_double) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val_double ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND CAST(2.5 AS DOUBLE) FOLLOWING)

g.title: t7
g.text: max(val_date) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val_date ASC NULLS FIRST RANGE BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 2 FOLLOWING)

g.title: t8

g.title: t9
g.text: sum(val) OVER (PARTITION BY cate ORDER BY val DESC NULLS LAST RANGE BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 1 FOLLOWING)
